fields.value: Replication data for: Common-Space Ideal Points, Committee Assignments, and Financial Interests in the State Legislatures

dsDescriptionValue.value: We present a new unified dataset of common-space ideal points, committee assignments, and financial interests for all state legislators in 1999. We describe the compilation of the dataset and offer a few possible applications.

publicationCitation.value: Battista, James C., Michael Peress, and Jesse Richman. 2013. "Common-Space Ideal Points, Committee Assignments, and Financial Interests in the State Legislatures." State Politics & Policy Quarterly 13(1):70-87.
